âEh, isnât it? I am going to give them some flesh, and living flesh,
too; not the bladders of lard that they turn out.â

âItâs a woman bathing, isnât it?â asked Sandoz.

âNo; I shall put some vine leaves around her head. A Bacchante, you
understand.â

At this Claude flew into a violent passion.

âA Bacchante? Do you want to make fools of people? Does such a thing as
