âYour machineâs very good too. Ah, my fine fellow, draughtsmanship has
no terrors for you!â

âNo, indeed,â declared Chaine, who had grown purple with vanity under
his black bushy beard.

He and Mahoudeau joined the band, and the latter asked the others
