school of the âopen air!ââ

Jory slapped his thighs.

âDidnât I tell you? I felt sure of making them bite with those articles
of mine, the idiots that they are. Ah! how weâll plague them now.â

Mahoudeau also was singing victory, constantly dragging in his
âVintaging Girl,â the daring points of which he explained to the silent
