âAh! yes, ah! yes,â repeated Dubuche, catching Claudeâs enthusiasm;
âthatâs what I want to accomplish, youâll see some day. Give me time to
succeed, and when Iâm my own master--ah! when Iâm my own master.â

Night was coming on apace, and Claude was growing more and more animated
